2013-01-19 20:41 +0000 [r379547]  Walter Doekes <walter+asterisk@wjd.nu>

	* configure, include/asterisk/autoconfig.h.in,
	  include/asterisk/compat.h, main/strcompat.c, configure.ac: Add
