	  with an encrypted video stream when support for video is disabled
	  and res_srtp is loaded. (closes issue ASTERISK-19202) Reported
	  by: Catalin Sanda

2012-01-18 20:54 +0000 [r351450]  Matthew Jordan <mjordan@digium.com>

