2010-10-18 21:55 +0000 [r292227]  Jeff Peeler <jpeeler@digium.com>

	* apps/app_voicemail.c, /: Merged revisions 292226 via svnmerge
	  from https://origsvn.digium.com/svn/asterisk/branches/1.6.2
