	  ................ r289704 | pabelanger | 2010-10-01 13:09:03 -0400
	  (Fri, 01 Oct 2010) | 13 lines Merged revisions 289703 via
	  svnmerge from
	  https://origsvn.digium.com/svn/asterisk/branches/1.4 ........
