	  implicitly unnecessarily, breaking builds

2010-06-03 00:02 +0000 [r267399]  Richard Mudgett <rmudgett@digium.com>

	* channels/sig_pri.h, channels/chan_dahdi.c,
	  configs/chan_dahdi.conf.sample, configure,
