2010-01-19 00:24 +0000 [r241187]  Alec L Davis <sivad.a@paradise.net.nz>

	* channels/sig_pri.c: Update CDR variables before pbx starts
	  (overlap dial) Allows CDR variables added in cdr.c:set_one_cid to
