2009-07-08 16:27 +0000 [r205196]  Tilghman Lesher <tlesher@digium.com>

	* /, main/say.c: Merged revisions 205188 via svnmerge from
	  https://origsvn.digium.com/svn/asterisk/branches/1.4 ........
