	  | 2 lines Remove the use of RTLD_NOLOAD, as it is not behaving
	  like expected. ........

	* /, main/asterisk.exports: Merged revisions 183238 via svnmerge
	  from https://origsvn.digium.com/svn/asterisk/branches/1.4
